bootstrap
=========
this is used for designing the responsive layout
responsive means adjustable to any device
step-1
add responsive related tags in head tag
  
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
step-2
add bootstrap css and js files in head tag
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  step-3
  start writting bootstrap classes 